<section id="gridftp-changes-summary">
  <title>Summary of Changes in GridFTP</title>
  <section>
    <title>New Features: GridFTP</title>
    <para>
      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-165">GRIDFTP-165</ulink>: MLSD response on the control channel</simpara>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-201">GRIDFTP-201</ulink>: Please give progress markers / heartbeats when doing CKSM</simpara>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-219">GRIDFTP-219</ulink>: allow PROT setting with non-gsi control channels</simpara>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-227">GRIDFTP-227</ulink>: Add server option to enable threaded operation and set number of threads.</simpara>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </para>
  </section>
  <section>
    <title>Improvements: GridFTP</title>
    <para>
      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-126">GRIDFTP-126</ulink>: globus-url-copy is sending unnecessary MKDs</simpara>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-198">GRIDFTP-198</ulink>: MLSC is very slow</simpara>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-199">GRIDFTP-199</ulink>: control chan lib (which fxp uses) very slow with large MLSC response</simpara>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-208">GRIDFTP-208</ulink>: Add manpage for globus-url-copy</simpara>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-209">GRIDFTP-209</ulink>: Add manpage for globus-gridftp-server</simpara>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-228">GRIDFTP-228</ulink>: Allow login without delegated credentials</simpara>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <simpara><ulink url="http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRIDFTP-230">GRIDFTP-230</ulink>: Suppress gfork error message</simpara>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </para>
